{"tid":2452536,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古印度的種姓制度  《一日森知識》","createTime":"2021-03-19T01:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T14:45:28.000Z","uid":129010,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afe9b1769e873810aa469e39e8288a4f25704d1d","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"古老的印度是世界四大文明發祥地之一。印度存在著一個森嚴的等級制度叫做&mdash;種姓制度。古印度將人們分成四個主要的種姓。前一種姓高於後一種姓。他們的權利、義務職業都不相同⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 影片連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8ucMLe9n1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8ucMLe9n1U&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=f2d8c931\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8ucMLe9n1U</a><br />\n<br />\n如果鐘意請比個Like, Subscribe！"},{"pid":"e764df5c37338b7e9b0ef4d9bbc6387c09cc4993","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"► 圖文版本<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guv5wc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fguv5wc1.jpg&h=b123ed8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTT3hTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTT3hTf.jpg&h=66d04116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古老的印度是世界四大文明發祥地之一。印度存在著一個森嚴的等級制度叫做&mdash;種姓制度。古印度將人們分成四個主要的種姓。前一種姓高於後一種姓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efT6Z9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefT6Z9k.jpg&h=ad516cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們的權利、義務職業都不相同⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKiKMMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKiKMMN.jpg&h=23b43fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCGPXTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCGPXTn.jpg&h=a602b72c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（只有我們可成為僧侶）<br />\n1. 社會地位是最高可以主宰一切的是：祭司貴族－婆羅門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayqk4yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fayqk4yn.jpg&h=4d6e9549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們主要掌握神權、占卜禍福，且壟斷文化和報導農時季節<br />\n（左：我們現在都改做教育/科學家；右：廚師也適合我們！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OW8t0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OW8t0b.jpg&h=e42e60c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2. 剎帝利－軍事貴族<br />\n（不是所有人都可以轉生！）<br />\n包括國王和各級武士、官吏。除了神權之外掌握一切國家權力，是世俗的統治者。地位僅次於婆羅門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0g5pMMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0g5pMMR.jpg&h=acdaa376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩個種姓的人靠剝削為生，構成古印度統治階級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUxjAFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUxjAFn.jpg&h=71cc11d1&s={SIZE}\" /> 接着是 3. 小生產者－吠舍<br />\n主要從事農牧業、手工業和商業。他們是自由民，向國家繳納賦稅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNOCnkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNOCnkn.jpg&h=f62935b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84cbe1caf1d2139241fbada782a2b6b101fe0a7e","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bjJ2ku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bjJ2ku.jpg&h=b466e69e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NV5xbdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNV5xbdP.jpg&h=3f23fb84&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最底的是 4. 首陀羅<br />\n指那些失去土地的自由民和被征服的原住民&mdash;達羅毗荼人。首陀羅人實際上處於奴隸地位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCGwrM9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCGwrM9.jpg&h=f5e76d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（轉職失敗圖示）<br />\n各個種姓職業世襲，有嚴格的界限。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUa1O0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUa1O0F.jpg&h=d8c99810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（低種姓男人竟想娶高種姓女生）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78g04Ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78g04Ah.jpg&h=1980247d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n種姓之間亦不能通婚。否則他們和其所生的子女不再屬於任何種姓，會被稱為賤民，或叫不可接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MncPdsv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMncPdsv.jpg&h=0b87454d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（左：禁食水煮食物；右：要在日出前完成）<br />\n賤民最受所有人鄙視。這些不可接觸者他們只能從事一些，最低賤的工作，例如：清理糞便與垃圾、洗衣、清掃等⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1mgCUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1mgCUe.jpg&h=2c7bc42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（不要進入本區！）<br />\n他們的身體和他們用過的東西被視為是最齷齪的。不能與婆羅門接觸。其他社會隔離如不能與其他種姓的人共用一口水井。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLtuXUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLtuXUj.jpg&h=1eb0e543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（這是我們的專用水井）<br />\n一些現今印度村落，如果不可接觸者家中有人出生，他們家人會痛哭，為其苦難的命運而悲傷，希望他早日轉生成高種姓的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tjwo2k5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftjwo2k5.jpg&h=7e322e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（今天一定會破財跟生病！）<br />\n婆羅門認為如果接觸了賤民會很倒楣，回去之後要舉行淨身儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qhqtt1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhqtt1a.jpg&h=90f72abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（要穿死人的衣服；要穿死人的衣服）<br />\n「賤民」要佩戴特殊的標記。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xRHysU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xRHysU.jpg&h=842284ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（禁用公用道路）<br />\n外出時要敲打破瓦罐之類的東西，或嘴裏要不斷發出特殊的聲音，以提醒其他種姓的人及時躲避自己。剎帝利和婆羅門偶然看見賤民會不能容忍，被碰見的賤民常常遭到他人毒打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13rz81j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F13rz81j.jpg&h=0e6d2fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他極端的情況：當見到一個婆羅門，賤民要立即平臥地上以免其「影子」玷污對方。"},{"pid":"e710147559b552eb6c4bcc5e9952b8da2af37533","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhUuds3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhUuds3.jpg&h=5e4fbcea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆羅門教宣稱把人分為四個種姓完全出於神的意志。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY0xbeN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY0xbeN.jpg&h=7a190096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在經典《吠陀》中，婆羅門用神話來解釋「種姓」的出現：說原始巨人普魯沙死後，天神梵天用他的嘴造出了婆羅門；用雙手製成了剎帝利；用雙腿製成了吠舍；用雙腳製成了首陀羅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiQX6Oe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiQX6Oe.png&h=2c7903af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以神話將種姓的貴賤之別，[講]成天經地義的。為了維護種姓制度奴隸主人還制定了許多法律。其中最典型的是《摩奴法典》。相傳，摩奴是大神梵天的兒子。為了確定人間不同的人們在社會上的應有次序，確定婆羅門和其他種姓的義務，於是制定了這部法典。<br />\n<br />\n《摩奴法典》首先確認：婆羅門是「一切創造物的主宰」。他們可以強迫首陀羅勞役。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a70X6OZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa70X6OZ.jpg&h=4812ea32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wZ9XVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wZ9XVK.jpg&h=cdae92ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（國王會放逐我若做非種姓規定的工作）<br />\n首陀羅必須要溫順地為其他種姓服務。禁止首陀羅累積個人財產。婆羅門亦有權奪取首陀羅的一切。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSak4Az.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSak4Az.jpg&h=a6309ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，低級種姓若動手傷害了高級種姓的人就須要斬斷其手；動腳的要斬斷腳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDYF4Au.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDYF4Au.jpg&h=429fea61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（本店不歡迎您們這些人）<br />\n其他社會規定如不同種姓的人不能同桌吃飯/共食，更不能在同一個房問裹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzzudtM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzzudtM.jpg&h=5d4714ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果一個年邁的剎帝利看到一個10歲的婆羅門也要像子對父般恭敬。血統高貴的人先可佩戴聖線之類⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9L8VTtG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L8VTtG.jpg&h=cbcf0ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然1950年印度獨立後，制定憲法去否定種姓制度。但是現實已經成為根深蒂固的社會習慣。在種姓以外的「賤民」生活更加困難。甘地亦極力提升賤民的地位，但亦未能將此舊俗習徹底廢除<br />\n<br />\n▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝▝<br />\n如果鐘意請比個Like, Subscribe！<br />\n<br />\n► 之前作品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2QLFiV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2QLFiV.png&h=1b6e439b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2438977/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2438977/page/1</a><br />\n全民皆兵的斯巴達人 《一日森知識》"},{"pid":"8352d44431fc31a73b15d567bde61303a4b3fbdb","tid":2452536,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:48:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾pr上嚟幫垃圾channel賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉"},{"pid":"37a4df660e74417923e8257c663dbeb9593c9f56","tid":2452536,"uid":232466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:58:43.000Z","msg":"宗教立國真係毒瘤嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0af698a0b33df5140f094e95ae5cd4b7f5e46f","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8352d44431fc31a73b15d567bde61303a4b3fbdb","tid":2452536,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:48:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾pr上嚟幫垃圾channel賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想有PR幫我宣傳⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nBtw，又唔拎住枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />武漢肺炎疫苗逼您like同subscribe"},{"pid":"89817016b3282f08298b5d0468688ce13d0baf77","tid":2452536,"uid":129138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e764df5c37338b7e9b0ef4d9bbc6387c09cc4993","tid":2452536,"uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"► 圖文版本<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guv5wc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fguv5wc1.jpg&h=b123ed8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTT3hTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTT3hTf.jpg&h=66d04116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古老的印度是世界四大文明發祥地之一。印度存在著一個森嚴的等級制度叫做&mdash;種姓制度。古印度將人們分成四個主要的種姓。前一種姓高於後一種姓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efT6Z9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefT6Z9k.jpg&h=ad516cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們的權利、義務職業都不相同⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKiKMMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKiKMMN.jpg&h=23b43fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCGPXTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCGPXTn.jpg&h=a602b72c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（只有我們可成為僧侶）<br />\n1. 社會地位是最高可以主宰一切的是：祭司貴族－婆羅門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayqk4yn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fayqk4yn.jpg&h=4d6e9549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們主要掌握神權、占卜禍福，且壟斷文化和報導農時季節<br />\n（左：我們現在都改做教育/科學家；右：廚師也適合我們！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OW8t0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OW8t0b.jpg&h=e42e60c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2. 剎帝利－軍事貴族<br />\n（不是所有人都可以轉生！）<br />\n包括國王和各級武士、官吏。除了神權之外掌握一切國家權力，是世俗的統治者。地位僅次於婆羅門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0g5pMMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0g5pMMR.jpg&h=acdaa376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩個種姓的人靠剝削為生，構成古印度統治階級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUxjAFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUxjAFn.jpg&h=71cc11d1&s={SIZE}\" /> 接着是 3. 小生產者－吠舍<br />\n主要從事農牧業、手工業和商業。他們是自由民，向國家繳納賦稅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNOCnkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNOCnkn.jpg&h=f62935b5&s={SIZE}\" />"}}